{"word":"Greece","slug":"greece","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Greece</b> Inhabitants of:<br/> - Called Gentiles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=7&verse=26'>Mar 7:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=7&verse=35'>Joh 7:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=2&verse=10'>Rom 2:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=3&verse=9'>Rom 3:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=10&verse=32'>1Co 10:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=12&verse=13'>1Co 12:13</a> <br/> - Desire to See <a href='S:Jesus, The Christ'>Jesus</a><br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=12&verse=23'>Joh 12:23</a> <br/> - Marry among the Jews<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=16&verse=1'>Act 16:1</a> <br/> - Accept the Messiah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=4'>Act 17:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=12'>Act 17:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=17&verse=34'>Act 17:34</a> <br/> - Persecute the early Christians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=6&verse=14'>Act 6:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=29'>Act 9:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=18&verse=17'>Act 18:17</a> <br/> - Gentiles called Greeks<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=10&verse=12'>Rom 10:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=3&verse=28'>Gal 3:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=3&verse=11'>Col 3:11</a> <br/> Schools of philosophy in Athens<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=19&verse=9'>Act 19:9</a><br/> Philosophy of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&ch